I got charged 9.25 for less of a wrap i always pay 5-5.50 in their other locations(Melrose, story). the Mexican gentleman behind the counter stated that's because they used 2 eggs.. all I did was smile. This location just lost a customer and believe me the word is going to get around. I'd be going to melas on Washington around the corner from the firehouse whenever I'm in the area from now on.
